machine_end_gcode:
G1 Z{min(max(50, max_layer_z+2), printable_height)} F600 ; move z up
G1 X{print_bed_max[0] - 5} Y{print_bed_max[1] / 2} F{travel_speed*60} ; move to middle right
M140 S0 ; turn off bed
M104 S0 ; turn off hotend
M107 ; turn off fan
M18 X Y E ; disable steppers
machine_start_gcode:
G90 ; use absolute coordinates
M83 ; extruder relative mode
M140 S[bed_temperature_initial_layer] ; set final bed temp
M104 S150 ; set temporary nozzle temp to prevent oozing during homing
G4 S10 ; allow partial nozzle warmup
G28 ; home all axis
M420 S1 L0 ; load mesh 0
G1 X5 Y5 F3000 ; move X Y 5
G1 Z0.28 F240 ; move Z 0.28
M104 S[nozzle_temperature_initial_layer] ; set final nozzle temp
M190 S[bed_temperature_initial_layer] ; wait for bed temp to stabilize
M109 S[nozzle_temperature_initial_layer] ; wait for nozzle temp to stabilize
G92 E0
G1 Y140 E10 F1500 ; prime the nozzle
G1 X2.3 F5000
G92 E0
G1 Y10 E10 F1200 ; prime the nozzle
G92 E0
